<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="297" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1437,1089,1801]" pageId="10" pageNumber="297">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,335,1596,1621]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="297" reason="1">Comments.</emphasis>
The genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="McLachlan" authorityYear="1898" box="[469,572,1596,1621]" class="Insecta" family="Ascalaphidae" genus="Bubopsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="297" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[469,572,1596,1621]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="297">Bubopsis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
comprises at least 8 species distributed in the Mediterranean Basin, Middle East and 
<collectingCountry box="[252,313,1632,1657]" name="India" pageId="10" pageNumber="297">India</collectingCountry>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Hagen, H. A." box="[324,478,1632,1657]" pageId="10" pageNumber="297" pagination="33 - 62" refId="ref16310" refString="Hagen, H. A. (1873) Die Larven von Ascalaphus. Stettiner Entomologische Zeitung, 34, 33 - 62." type="journal article" year="1873">Hagen (1873)</bibRefCitation>
described for the first time a larva of this genus as “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Rambur, 1842" authorityName="Rambur" authorityYear="1842" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1767" box="[1058,1361,1632,1657]" class="Insecta" family="Ascalaphidae" genus="Theleproctophylla" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="297" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="barbara">
<emphasis box="[1058,1361,1632,1657]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="297">Theleproctophylla barbara</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
” as he identified the specimen only on a geographic basis, ignoring the presence of the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="McLachlan" authorityYear="1898" box="[1144,1247,1668,1693]" class="Insecta" family="Ascalaphidae" genus="Bubopsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="297" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1144,1247,1668,1693]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="297">Bubopsis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<collectingCountry box="[1285,1385,1668,1693]" name="Turkey" pageId="10" pageNumber="297">Anatolia</collectingCountry>
. His description is accurate enough to assign it to this genus for certain, as also suggested by 
<bibRefCitation author="Escribano, C." box="[1151,1349,1704,1729]" pageId="10" pageNumber="297" pagination="365 - 370" refId="ref16154" refString="Escribano, C. (1921) Desarrollo de la Theleproctophylla (Neuropt.). In: Tomo Extraordinario Publicado con Motivo del 50 ° Aniversario de su Fundacion. Real Sociedad Espanola de Historia Natural, Madrid, pp. 365 - 370." type="book chapter" year="1921">Escribano (1921)</bibRefCitation>
. Over a century later, the larva of 
<taxonomicName authority="U. Aspock, H. Aspock &amp; Holzel, 1979" authorityName="U. Aspock, H. Aspock &amp; Holzel" authorityYear="1979" box="[466,1122,1740,1765]" class="Insecta" family="Ascalaphidae" genus="Bubopsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="297" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="andromache">
<emphasis box="[466,642,1740,1765]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="297">B. andromache</emphasis>
U. Aspöck, H. Aspöck &amp; Hölzel, 1979
</taxonomicName>
was finally described and illustrated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Pieper, H. &amp; Willmann, R." box="[305,608,1776,1801]" pageId="10" pageNumber="297" pagination="1 - 11" refId="ref17155" refString="Pieper, H. &amp; Willmann, R. (1980) Die Larven griechischer Ascalaphiden-Arten (Ins., Planipennia). Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde, 337, 1 - 11." type="journal article" year="1980">Pieper &amp; Willmann (1980)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
